<p>Next project was about adding a &lsquo;Banner&rsquo; for category archive pages. The following is the category banner uploader.</p>

<p><img class='center' src="http://uw-freelancer.github.io/images/blog/wordpress-category-banner.jpg" title="Category Banner Uploader" alt="Category Banner Uploader" /></p>

<p>I was able to successfully complete the project and earned $27USD.</p>

